                        "escape"
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        "2": {
            "text": "You are travelling along a narrow section of coast road which follows a dizzy\ncourse beneath high, overhanging cliffs. A rockfall has blocked the road ahead\nand you must stop to clear it. You are helping the driver to lever a large rock\nfrom the path of the carriage, when you hear the sound of falling rocks. A\nboulder crashes down from the overhanging cliff, killing the driver before you\ncan make any attempt to save him. He was standing less than six feet away from\nyou at the time of his death.",
