        "11": {
            "text": "Covering yourself with your Kai cloak, you hide inside a large wooden barrel.\nBut it is to no avail, for in less than a minute the trapdoor is thrown open and\nfour angry villagers drop to the stone floor, torches and swords held high in\ntheir hands. As you are dragged kicking from the cellar, the screams of the\ncrowd drown your pleas for mercy.",
            "choices": []
