        "14": {
            "text": "As the contest begins, you use your Kai Discipline to weaken your opponent's\nconcentration. Beads of sweat stand out on his forehead and his eyes gradually\nclose as he withers under your relentless Mindblast. In less than a minute he\nhas collapsed to the floor completely unconscious.",
