        "19": {
            "text": "Less than twenty yards away, a small search party is marching along the wet\ncobblestones. You run towards the darkened doorway of a small shop and quickly\nenter to avoid the mob. With your heart pounding in your chest, you pray that\nyou have not been spotted.",
