        "23": {
            "text": "You chase the furry creature as it hurries along a narrow, twisting passage for\nnearly ten minutes and are about to give up the chase when the passage opens out\ninto a huge torchlit cavern. A stunning sight greets your eyes. The cavern\nhouses an entire colony of these strange creatures, all busy sorting through and\nexamining a vast pile of strange objects littering the centre of the hall.",
