        "24": {
            "text": "It is the crypt of Killean the Overlord. He had been ruler of Ragadorn, but he\nand many others in Ragadorn died during an outbreak of Red Death plague three\nyears ago.\n\nYou suddenly recall a journeyman of your monastery called Swift Fox. He told you\ntales of his many travels to Ragadorn. The Red Death killed over half the\npopulation here. It also killed Swift Fox.",
