        "25": {
            "text": "Casting your eye around the crowded tavern, you notice that many of the local\nvillagers are playing various gambling games. Near to the main door, a young\nrogue has three upturned wooden cups on the table in front of him. He spins them\naround and challenges anyone to point out the cup that contains a small glass\nmarble. If they guess correctly, he will pay them double the money they have\ngambled.",
