            "text": "The food tastes delicious and it is only a matter of minutes before you empty\nyour plate. You decide to take a short nap before meeting the others in the bar\nroom. But as you are about to lie down, a terrible pain grips your stomach. Your\nlegs buckle and you fall trembling to the floor. You feel as if your whole body\nis on fire. One word repeats itself over and over again in your mind-\npoison...poison...poison...",
