            "text": "You are in luck, for the boat has seen your distress signal and is heading\ntowards you. It is a small fishing boat from the port of Ragadorn. The fishermen\nare a rough-looking bunch, but they wrap you in a warm blanket and offer you\nsome food. The captain suggests that you sleep, as it will be two or three hours\nbefore they arrive back in Ragadorn.\n\nhttp://www.projectaon.org/en/xhtml/lw/02fotw//small6.png[Illustration]",
