        "43": {
            "text": "You swing the Sommerswerd in a wide arc and hit four of the zombies in one\nsweep, but no sooner do their corpses drop to the deck than others press forward\nto take their place. You will never kill them all before they overwhelm you. As\nthey start to tear at your cloak, you are forced to dive overboard into the sea\nto avoid certain death.",
