        "48": {
            "text": "Pointing at a jug of ale on the bar, you tell the sailor to watch very closely.\nClosing your eyes, you concentrate on the jug until you can picture it in your\nmind's eye. As you will the jug to rise in the air, you hear the sailor gasp in\namazement.",
