        "67": {
            "text": "You quickly deduce that the impostor must have escaped by the main entrance to\nthe tavern, and if he is still in the harbour area he must be in or around the\nmain square.\n\nYou search the buildings and alleyways round the square but there is no sign of\nhim at all. Rather than waste more time in a fruitless search, you return to the\nquayside and untie a small coracle from its mooring. As you row towards the\nGreen Sceptre you begin to feel uneasy that so early in your mission your\nenemies seem already to have found you.",
