        "68": {
            "text": "The guard's expression changes to a sneer of contempt. \"I am a soldier of\nDurenor. Your gold will not help you here.\"\n\nUnfortunately you have insulted his honour and he intends to teach you a harsh\nlesson.",
            "choices": [
