        "77": {
            "text": "During the period of your Kai training, your masters taught you many of the\nlanguages and dialects of northern Magnamund, one of which was Szall. The\ncreatures in this clearing are Szalls and they are screaming at you that the\nwounded man is not a man at all. They say he is a Helghast, a powerful shape-\nchanging servant of the Darklords.",
