        "92": {
            "text": "The hideous creature lets out one last cry as it collapses at your feet. As you\nstep back to avoid the putrid smell of its rotting corpse, you see three more\nHelghast advancing towards you. To remain here would be suicide. You shout a\nwarning to Rhygar as you turn and flee for the safety of the woods.",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "text": "Turn to 183.",
                    "section": "183"
                }
