        "94": {
            "text": "You urge the captain to investigate the vessel, but he ignores your plea and\norders the crew to continue with their duties. As the trading ship disappears\nfrom view, you stare at it and wonder why the captain was so reluctant to do\nanything.\n\nYou descend below deck and take care to lock the door of your cabin behind you.",
