                    "text": "Turn to 240.",
                    "section": "240"
                }
            ]
        },
        "95": {
            "text": "You spur your horse through the tangle of trees until you enter a small\nclearing. Six Szalls are jumping excitedly around the writhing body of a man on\nthe ground. A strangely carved spear is stuck in his chest, and lying dead\nbeside him is the body of a Knight of the White Mountain. The creatures are\nshrieking at each other and appear to be unconcerned with the man's obvious\nagony.\n\nhttp://www.projectaon.org/en/xhtml/lw/02fotw//small11.png[Illustration]",
            "alternate_choices": true,
