        "97": {
            "text": "You have noticed during your rigorous training exercises with the Sommerswerd\nthat your Kai Discipline of Sixth Sense has become more sensitive than ever\nbefore: you knew exactly what Madin Rendalim's sad news was long before he\nactually told you. You may find that your improved Sixth Sense will be an\nimportant advantage upon your return to Holmgard.",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "text": "Turn to 152.",
                    "section": "152"
                }
            ]
        },
        "98": {
            "text": "Your Kai sense reveals that there are no tracks in this part of the Durenor\nForest, but it does tell you the correct direction to Port Bax. However, the\nforest that lies before you is so dense that you will have to abandon your horse\nat the watchtower before you can continue.",
            "alternate_choices": true,
            "choices": [
