        "104": {
            "text": "The fishermen stare at you with open mouths as if they have just seen a corpse\nreturn from the dead. Suddenly one of them kicks over the table and they make\ntheir escape through the back door of the tavern. In one bound, you leap over\nthe table and pursue them out of the tavern, into the darkness beyond.",
