        "107": {
            "text": "The captain orders his crew to go alongside. As they board the trader, you are\nshocked by the sight that awaits you. Dead sailors cover the deck, many pierced\nby arrows. It seems they must have put up a desperate fight to defend their\ncargo, but not a trace of it remains in any of the ship's holds. Below deck, you\ndiscover the captain in his cabin. He is very badly wounded and near to death.",
