        "111": {
            "text": "The guards reluctantly lower their weapons and allow you to cross the bridge. As\nyou slip past, they stare at you and whisper to each other. Once you are safely\nacross the Rymerift, you quickly hurry on your way in case they change their\nminds and arrest you. After nearly an hour of walking along the forest road, you\narrive at a junction where a signpost points to the east.\n\n                                Port Bax-3 Miles\n\nYou smile and set off eastwards. You should be there in just under an hour.",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "text": "Turn to 265.",
                    "section": "265"
                }
            ]
        },
        "112": {
            "text": "You suddenly remember what he said about the shop with the orange door. It is\nthe headquarters of the Silent Brotherhood, Lachlan's notorious secret police.\nTo enter here would be more perilous than entering a roomful of Drakkarim!\n\nYou quickly turn away from the orange door and hurry northwards.",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "text": "Turn to 230.",
                    "section": "230"
                }
            ]
        },
        "113": {
            "text": "He is Vonotar the Traitor, renegade wizard from the Magicians' Guild of Toran.\nHe is a master of the black arts and now possesses great power which the\nDarklords themselves have given him. It was his agents who tried to assassinate\nyou during your quest, and it is he who commands the death-hulk fleet. Destroy\nVonotar and you will destroy the evil force that gives power to the death-hulks\nand their crews.",
            "alternate_choices": true,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "text": "You may climb the tower and attack Vonotar by turning to 73.",
                    "section": "73",
                    "words": [
