        "123": {
            "text": "A strange power is coursing through your body. Instinctively you raise the blade\nabove your head and a shaft of sunlight suddenly catches the edge of the sword\nand floods the King's chamber with a blinding white glow.\n\nBut almost immediately the light starts to fade and you are aware of Lord Axim's\nhand upon your shoulder. \"Come, Lone Wolf. There is much to prepare for your\nreturn to Sommerlund.\"\n\nYou sheathe the Sommerswerd in its jewelled scabbard and follow Lord Axim as he\nturns and leaves the King's chamber.",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "text": "Turn to 40.",
                    "section": "40"
                }
            ]
        },
