        "128": {
            "text": "A golden glow runs the length of the Sommerswerd as you raise it high above your\nhead, ready to face your enemy. You are confronted by six grisly zombies and you\nmust fight them as one enemy.\n\nZombie Crew: COMBAT SKILL 13, ENDURANCE 19\n\nThey are undead creatures, so remember to double all ENDURANCE points they lose\nas a result of the power of the Sommerswerd.",
