                    "section": "4"
                }
            ]
        },
        "130": {
            "text": "The priest approaches you and says, \"You need to rest, as we all do. I\nunderstand your problem my friend. Please allow me to practice what I humbly\npreach,\" and with these words he leads you to the bar and places a Gold Crown\ninto the hand of the innkeeper. \"A room for my friend,\" he says and smiles.",
            "choices": [
