        "132": {
            "text": "You crash to the muddy street in a shower of broken glass. You are winded by the\nfall, but otherwise unharmed. An angry villager armed with a cudgel tries to\nsmash your skull, but you roll aside, jump to your feet and sprint away down the\ntwisting street before he has struck his blow. Then an ugly Szall on horseback\ncharges towards you with a raised spear. He is about to stab you when you\nsidestep and grab the weapon, pulling it and the Szall from the saddle.\n\nIf you wish to keep the Spear, remember to mark it on your Action Chart.",
