        "133": {
            "text": "Looking directly into the sailor's eyes, you concentrate your Mindblast at his\nopen hand. Suddenly the man falls backwards from his chair, clutching his hand\nas if he had just picked up a red-hot coal. When you explain what has happened\nto him, he looks at you in amazement.",
