        "134": {
            "text": "Suddenly from out of the darkness there is a blood-chilling cry. You find\nyourself staring into the glowing eyes of a Helghast. As it tries to close its\nfingers around your throat, you scream in terror and fall to the ground. The\nhideous creature tears at your tunic, rending the cloth with its black claws.\n\nhttp://www.projectaon.org/en/xhtml/lw/02fotw//ill8.png[Illustration]: You find yourself staring into the glowing eyes of a Helghast.",
