        "135": {
            "text": "The knight points to the woods behind you and says in a gruff voice, \"There is\nyour shelter.\"\n\nBefore you can reply, he has stepped back into the tower and bolted the heavy\ndoor. The forest here is very dense and the undergrowth is a tangle of weeds and\nbriars. It will prove impossible to enter the wood on horseback, so you must\nabandon your mount before continuing on foot.",
