        "139": {
            "text": "The training that you received in the art of Hunting has taught you to recognize\nmost of the poisonous and non-poisonous fruits to be found in northern\nMagnamund. These purple fruits are larnuma, a sweet and nutritious food. You\nquickly eat your fill and then store enough of them in your Backpack for 2\nMeals.\n\nBeyond the larnuma trees, you notice a wide coast road that disappears towards\nthe east and the west.",
