        "143": {
            "text": "You head south and follow the quayside until you come to a junction where the\nstreet heads off towards the east. Most of the shops in this street are still\nclosed except for one to your right. There is a sign above the door.\n\n            Jinelda Koop-Alchemist: Magical Potions Bought and Sold",
