            "text": "The crew's quarters are cramped and stifling. But despite a lack of space and a\npoor evening meal (so poor in fact that you lose 2 ENDURANCE points!) the men\nare pleased that their invitation was accepted and you are treated as an\nhonoured guest.\n\nAfter supper, they invite you to play \"Portholes\" with them, and wager a little\ngold on the fall of the dice.",
