        "166": {
            "text": "You make your way up a flight of stairs and onto the crowded deck. Fierce battle\nrages all around you as the Durenese fleet is engulfed by the rush of ghostly\ndeath-hulks. Suddenly a flash of searing flame shoots from a tower at the rear\nof the death-hulk you are on, and explodes into the side of a Durenese warship\nless than fifty yards away. You watch with horror as soldiers leap from the\ndeck, their clothes and hair in flames.\n\nhttp://www.projectaon.org/en/xhtml/lw/02fotw//ill10.png[Illustration]: Soldiers leap from the deck, their clothes and hair in flames.",
            "alternate_choices": true,
