        "175": {
            "is_random_pick": true,
            "text": "\"It seems our bird has flown,\" says the captain, pointing to a longboat moving\nswiftly towards another ship on the horizon. \"She flies no flag, and her hull is\nof a strange shape. I've ne'er before seen the like.\"\n\nYou watch as the longboat reaches the mysterious ship. As if by magic a sea fog\nappears from nowhere and engulfs the vessel. Moments later, both the ship and\nthe fog have disappeared.\n\nPick a number from the Random Number Table.",
