            "text": "A quick search of their bodies reveals the following items:\n\n* 2 Spears\n\n* 2 Swords\n\n* 6 Gold Crowns\n\nIf you decide to take any of these, remember to mark them on your Action Chart.\n\nYou roll the bodies into the Rymerift and then run across the bridge in case\nanyone saw the incident. The forest track continues for over an hour before you\narrive at a junction, where you see a signpost.\n\n                                Port Bax-3 Miles\n\nYou adjust your equipment and set off towards the east.",
