        "190": {
            "text": "Using the edge of a steel rule to prise open the lock, you suddenly feel a sharp\npain in your chest. A cunning trap has been laid, and as you open the box, a\nsmall needle shoots out and embeds itself in your flesh. It is tipped with a\ndeadly poison. You die instantly.",
