        "191": {
            "text": "At the end of the avenue, the cobbled street turns abruptly to the right.\nOpposite this point is a tall, white stone building with a plaque above the\ndoor.\n\nhttp://www.projectaon.org/en/xhtml/lw/02fotw//small20.png[Illustration]: Port Watchtower-Harbour Authority\n\nYou can see that the cobbled street ends at a high stone wall. There is a large\nred gate in this wall and it is guarded by two soldiers. Beyond the gate, you\ncan make out the masts of ships moored in the harbour.",
