        "197": {
            "is_random_pick": true,
            "text": "As dawn breaks, a fierce storm rises and you are woken by the violent rocking of\nthe ship. The floor of your cabin is awash, and the shouts of the crew can\nhardly be heard above the howling wind. You quickly dress, gather up your\nequipment, and make your way to the deck.\n\nYou are soon joined by the captain, who takes hold of your arm and orders you to\nreturn to your cabin. Suddenly, as you start to go down, there is a thunderous\ncrack as, high in the rigging, part of the mast snaps. You look up to see the\nshattered pole falling towards you.\n\nPick a number from the Random Number Table.",
