            "text": "You have covered less than twenty yards when your horse rears up and bolts. You\nare thrown to the ground and you lose 1 ENDURANCE point. Brushing the dirt from\nyour cloak, you curse as the animal disappears out of sight. You will have to\ncontinue your journey from here on foot.",
