                    "text": "Turn to 31.",
                    "section": "31"
                }
            ]
        },
        "203": {
            "text": "\"Feeling hungry?\" you say, peering at the two busy house mice in the far corner.\n\"Perhaps you would care for some cheese?\"\n\nUsing your Kai Discipline, you order the two mice to bring the cheese to you.\nThe sailor looks on in amazement as the two furry creatures deposit the cheese\nat your feet and then scurry away.",
