        "204": {
            "text": "The keen sight you have developed through your Kai Discipline of Tracking has\nenabled you to identify the talisman that sits on top of the black staff. It is\nthe crescent and crystal star emblem of the Magicians' Guild of Toran in\nnorthern Sommerlund. This man is a renegade of the guild and a traitor to your\ncountry.",
