        "205": {
            "text": "The innkeeper frowns at you and points to a side door. \"If you can't afford a\nroom, you can go and sleep in the stable.\"\n\nAs you walk towards the exit, you feel the stare of the other passengers burning\ninto your back. The door is slammed shut and you stand shivering in the cold\nnight air.",
