            "is_random_pick": true,
            "text": "You place both hands on your stomach and try to fight back the pain as you\nconcentrate on focusing your skill. The familiar warmth of your healing power\nnumbs the pain, but the poison is very strong and your struggle is not yet over.\n\nPick a number from the Random Number Table. May the luck of the gods steer your\nchoice, for your life now hangs on the number that you pick.",
