        "230": {
            "text": "You follow the street until it turns abruptly eastwards into Beggar Lane. You\ncan see how this street got its name, for there are scores of ragged men, women,\nand children huddled in doorways, all holding out their begging bowls.\n\nhttp://www.projectaon.org/en/xhtml/lw/02fotw//small23.png[Illustration]\n\nAs you walk towards the junction at the end of the street, you are assailed from\nall sides with pleas for gold.",
