        "234": {
            "text": "Before you can defend yourself, the Helghast has smashed into you and you both\nfall onto the highway below.\n\nIt may be some comfort to learn that your death was swift and painless. Your\nneck was instantly broken and you were spared the agony of the Helghast's black\nfingers tearing and burning their way through your throat. The Seal of Hammerdal\nis now on its way to Holmgard, which will now fall to the Darklords.",
            "choices": []
