        "237": {
            "text": "The dead zombies lie around your feet. By now, the soldiers' fear of the undead\nhas turned to sheer hatred. A chorus of Durenese battle-cries resounds along the\ndeck. You lead the charge along a boarding plank and onto the deck of the death-\nhulk, cleaving the zombie crew aside like a scythe through wheat. Then suddenly\na black-cloaked figure blocks your path, a twisted sword held in its shrunken\nblack hand. It is a Helghast, and you must fight it to the death.\n\nHelghast: COMBAT SKILL 23, ENDURANCE 30\n\nIt is an undead creature, so remember to double all ENDURANCE points that it\nloses as a result of your possessing the Sommerswerd. It is immune to Mindblast.",
