            "text": "After three uneventful days at sea, you find shipboard life rather dreary. If\nyou have the Kai Discipline of Healing, any ENDURANCE points that you may have\nlost on your adventure so far are restored. This will bring your ENDURANCE\npoints score back to your original one. If you do not possess the skill, restore\nhalf of any points you have lost in combat.\n\nhttp://www.projectaon.org/en/xhtml/lw/02fotw//small24.png[Illustration]\n\nOn the afternoon of the fourth day, you are talking with an injured sailor up on\ndeck when you smell smoke seeping from the hold.",
