            "text": "A hush descends on the tavern as the man you have accused turns to face you.\n\n\"You've got a careless tongue, stranger,\" he says menacingly. \"It should be cut\nout before it does any more harm.\" He draws a curved dagger and attacks you. The\ncrowd form a circle around you both, preventing either of you from escaping. You\nmust fight this man to the death.\n\nTrickster: COMBAT SKILL 17, ENDURANCE 25",
