                    },
                    "words": [
                        "evade",
                        "running"
                    ],
                    "text": "If you do not want to fight, you can evade by running into the woods before\ncombat begins by turning to 183.",
                    "section": "183"
                }
            ]
        },
        "255": {
            "text": "Taking hold of your weapon, you demonstrate the Kai skills of balance and speed,\nas taught to you by your Kai masters. With breathtaking speed, as you spin and\ntwist the weapon around your head and body, the movement of your hands becomes a\ndazzling blur. To finish your display of Weaponskill, you strike the edge of a\npewter plate and send it spinning across the room so fast that it embeds itself\nin the cellar door.\n\nThe sailor watches in amazement.",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "text": "Turn to 268.",
                    "section": "268"
                }
            ]
        },
        "256": {
            "text": "You pass the stone steps and continue along the highway. You have just passed\nunder the platform when you hear a noise above you. You stop and stare upwards\nbut you can see nothing in the gloom of the tunnel ceiling.",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "text": "Turn to 134.",
                    "section": "134"
                }
            ]
        },
        "257": {
            "text": "This rubbish-strewn cobbled street runs between rows of ramshackle, rot-infested\nhouses and shops. The few inhabitants of Ragadorn that you see appear a\ncheerless lot, their faces haggard and drawn. They shuffle through the gloom,\nhunched against the pouring rain, their eyes fixed on the cobblestones at their\nfeet. Then you reach a junction where Axe Lane bends towards the north and\nanother street heads off towards the east.\n\nhttp://www.projectaon.org/en/xhtml/lw/02fotw//small25.png[Illustration]",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "text": "If you wish to continue north and enter Black Knight Street, turn to 335.",
                    "section": "335",
                    "words": [
                        "continue",
                        "north",
                        "enter",
                        "black",
                        "knight",
                        "street"
                    ]
