        "268": {
            "text": "\"You are indeed a Kai Lord,\" says the sailor, but the astonishment on his face\nquickly changes to an unpleasant sneer.\n\n\"Or should I say you were!\"\n\nhttp://www.projectaon.org/en/xhtml/lw/02fotw//ill16.png[Illustration]: You turn to see three harbour thugs advancing towards you.\n\nAs he speaks, a door crashes open behind you and you turn to see three harbour\nthugs advancing towards you. Each is armed with a scimitar and you have no\nchoice but to fight all three as one enemy.\n\nHarbour Thugs: COMBAT SKILL 16, ENDURANCE 25",
