        "269": {
            "text": "The horrific sight of the writhing creature fills you with loathing for the\nDarklords and their evil minions.\n\nWhen the Helghast has finally crumbled to nothing and you are quite sure that it\nhas been destroyed, you remove the Magic Spear and wipe the tip on its\nsmouldering robe.\n\nAnxious to leave this place, you run down the tunnel as fast as you can.",
