        "270": {
            "text": "Ganon rolls away from his chair and draws his sword. An instant later his\nbrother Dorier is by his side. You must fight them both as one enemy.\n\nGanon + Dorier: COMBAT SKILL 28, ENDURANCE 30\n\nDue to the surprise of your attack, add 2 points to your COMBAT SKILL for the\nfirst round of combat only. Because of their exceptional strength of will, they\nare immune to Mindblast.",
