        },
        "272": {
            "text": "Someone or something is approaching the door of the hold from the other side. If\nyou climb out through the shattered deck, you will leave your legs vulnerable to\nattack from below and there is no other way out. You sense that it is an evil\ncreature of some considerable power. Raise the Sommerswerd and prepare for\ncombat.",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "text": "Turn to 5.",
                    "section": "5"
                }
            ]
        },
        "273": {
            "text": "You are about to strike when your assailant shouts, \"I am Ronan, my lord. I mean\nyou no harm.\"\n\nYou manage to divert your blow at the last moment and your weapon smashes the\nback of a wooden chair. The beads of sweat that have broken out on the sailor's\nface appear to confirm that he speaks the truth.",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "text": "Lower your weapon and turn to 160.",
                    "section": "160",
                    "words": [
                        "lower",
                        "weapon"
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        "274": {
            "text": "A quick search of the bodies reveals a Sword, 6 Gold Crowns, and a Mace. Take\nwhat you wish and mark them on your Action Chart.\n\nBefore you can leave by the front door, more angry villagers have forced their\nway into the shop. You can only leave now by the first-floor window.",
            "items": [
                {
                    "name": "Sword",
                    "ac_section": "weapons"
                },
                {
                    "value": 6,
                    "name": "Gold Crowns",
                    "ac_section": "gold"
