        "275": {
            "text": "You become weaker and weaker until your body finally surrenders to the welcoming\narms of death. Your assassin has successfully completed his mission.",
            "choices": []
        },
        "276": {
            "text": "A grim-looking sailor is challenging all-comers to an arm-wrestling contest. He\nis so confident of winning that he will pay 5 Gold Crowns to anyone who beats\nhim. As you approach his table, a serving girl whispers in your ear, \"Be careful\nstranger, he is an evil man. He breaks the arms of those who lose, and murders\nany who beat him.\"\n\nhttp://www.projectaon.org/en/xhtml/lw/02fotw//small26.png[Illustration]\n\nAs you face the sailor across the table, bets are made throughout the tavern.\n\nIf you do not have this skill, conduct the wrestling contest as if you were in\ncombat. The first one to reach 0 ENDURANCE points, loses the match.\n\nSailor: COMBAT SKILL 18, ENDURANCE 25\n\nWhen the contest is over, restore your ENDURANCE points to the same total that\nyou had before the contest.",
            "is_special": true,
