        "279": {
            "text": "You recognize the creature to be a Noodnic, an intelligent but mischievous\nmountain-dwelling native of Durenor. The Noodnics inhabit a maze of smaller\nshafts and fissures that honeycomb the Hammerdal Mountains, and live off\nwhatever they can steal from the merchant caravans that travel the Tarnalin. It\noccurs to you that if you can catch the Noodnic, you may be able to learn if the\nHelghast are hiding within the tunnel.",
            "alternate_choices": true,
            "choices": [
