                    "section": "108",
                    "range": [
                        5,
                        9
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        "281": {
            "text": "You beg the captain to pick up the unfortunate castaways but he ignores your\npleas and orders the crew to continue with their duties. As the longboat\ndisappears from view, you have a premonition that a similar fate awaits you.\nShaken by the thought, you descend below decks and retire to your cabin.",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "text": "Turn to 240.",
                    "section": "240"
                }
            ]
        },
        "282": {
            "text": "Both soldiers stab at you with their spears and try to force you off the bridge.\nAs you lash out at one, the other dodges past you and attacks you from behind.\n\nYou cannot evade and you must fight them both to the death.\n\nBridge Guard 1: COMBAT SKILL 16, ENDURANCE 24\n\nBridge Guard 2: COMBAT SKILL 16, ENDURANCE 24",
            "combat": {
                "win": {
