                    "section": "32"
                }
            ]
        },
        "298": {
            "text": "You hear the footsteps behind you quicken, and you spin round just in time to\nsee them draw their daggers to attack you. You must deduct 4 points from your\nCOMBAT SKILL and fight them open-handed. They attack you one at a time.\n\nStreet Thief Leader: COMBAT SKILL 15, ENDURANCE 23\n\nStreet Thief 1: COMBAT SKILL 15, ENDURANCE 23\n\nStreet Thief 2: COMBAT SKILL 15, ENDURANCE 23",
            "combat": {
