        "302": {
            "text": "Stepping over the body, you set about a quick search of these living quarters.\nYou find:\n\n* Mace\n\n* Broadsword\n\n* Quarterstaff\n\n* Healing Potion (restores 3 ENDURANCE points)\n\n* Enough Food for 3 Meals\n\n* Backpack\n\n* 12 Gold Crowns\n\nTake whatever items you wish and quickly leave the watchtower in case someone\ndiscovers you.\n\nYou realize that the forest is very thick in this area and you will have to\nabandon your horse and continue on foot.",
