        "303": {
            "text": "Piles of rotting garbage litter this stretch of the waterfront, giving off such\nan evil smell that you are forced to cover your mouth and nose with your cloak.\nAhead to your left, you notice the glow of torchlight streaming from an open\ndoor. Above the door is a sign.\n\nhttp://www.projectaon.org/en/xhtml/lw/02fotw//small28.png[Illustration]: Ragadorn Trading Post-Merchandise Bought and Sold",
