        "313": {
            "text": "The gruesome death-cries of the Helghast finally fade and you risk stopping for\na few seconds to catch your breath. You wince as you discover that the\ncreature's fingers have burnt into your neck. The wounds are very sore and\npainful and you must lose 4 ENDURANCE points. Tearing the edge of your tunic,\nyou make a bandage before continuing on your journey through the Tarnalin\ntunnel. (Erase the Magic Spear from your Action Chart.)",
            "is_special": true,
            "endurance": -4,
            "choices": [
                {
