        "322": {
            "text": "There is a strong aura of evil surrounding these cloaked riders. Your Kai sense\nwarns you not to follow Rhygar and his men on their impetuous charge. You shout\na warning to them to stop them attacking, but it is too late. You cannot be\nheard above their battle-cries and the thundering hooves of their mounts.",
