        "326": {
            "text": "The captain orders the crew to hoist all the sails to attempt to outrun the\nvessel, but the pirate ship is fast and is trying to cross the bows of the Green\nSceptre. A collision seems imminent.\n\n\"Prepare to ram,\" the captain cries, as the side of the red-sailed warship looms\nup directly in front of the prow. There is an enormous crack of splintered\ntimber as the Green Sceptre punches a large hole into the side of the pirate\nship, and you are thrown to the deck with a jolt.\n\nhttp://www.projectaon.org/en/xhtml/lw/02fotw//ill19.png[Illustration]: The black-clad shape of a Drakkarim warrior is advancing towards\nyou, a large broadsword raised.\n\nAs the pirates clamber aboard, you are horrified to see the black-clad shape of\na Drakkarim warrior in their midst. He has spotted you and he is advancing\ntowards you, a large broadsword raised above his head. You must fight him to the\ndeath.\n\nDrakkar: COMBAT SKILL 15, ENDURANCE 25",
