                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        "327": {
            "text": "You are slowly walking back along the cobbled street, trying to think of the\nbest course of action, when a young boy approaches you. \"I can get you into the\nharbour, mister,\" he says, \"but it'll cost you.\"\n\nHe produces an envelope containing a sheaf of official-looking papers. \"These'll\nget you a red pass at the port watchtower. All yours for only 6 Gold Crowns.\"\n\nIf you wish to buy the documents, pay the boy 6 Gold Crowns. If you refuse them,\nhe will soon lose interest in you and will disappear. When you have made your\ndecision, you return to the port watchtower.",
            "alternate_choices": true,
            "items": [
                {
                    "gold_max": 6,
                    "name": "Documents",
                    "ac_section": "special_items"
                }
