        "328": {
            "text": "Two zombies try to block your passage but you cleave them in half with one sweep\nof the Sommerswerd. You are at the foot of the tower and you can now see a\nhunchbacked man in crimson robes above you. He wears a tall, curved tokmor, a\nmagician's head-dress. It bears the emblem of a serpent. In his right hand is a\nblack staff.",
