        "329": {
            "text": "\"Congratulations, Lone Wolf,\" says the captain, as he wipes the sweat from his\nfurrowed brow, \"you are a masterful player.\"\n\nHe reaches into his waistcoat pocket and hands you a small pouch containing 10\nGold Crowns. You thank him for the game and offer him the chance to win back his\nstake the following evening. With a wry smile, he accepts your offer and bids\nyou goodnight.",
