        "334": {
            "text": "After a few miles, the track becomes tangled and overgrown, until all trace of\nit has completely disappeared. The ride becomes slow and difficult as you strain\nto avoid the bogs and pot-holes of this moor.\n\nAfter several hours you reach the edge of Durenor Forest, and above the ferns,\nyou notice a tall watchtower. A spiral of smoke rises lazily from a hidden\nchimney.",
