        "336": {
            "text": "In a fraction of a second, the searing burst of flame changes direction in mid-\nair and is drawn towards the blade of the Sommerswerd. The bolt of energy\ndisappears into the golden blade like water into a drain. (You remember that the\nSommerswerd has the power to absorb magic. This power has saved you from certain\ndeath.)\n\nThe sorcerer curses you, pulls a jewel from his ornate tokmor, and throws it at\nyour feet. There is a flash of flame and a cloud of choking green gas billows up\nin your face, filling your nostrils with its acidic smell. You are forced to\njump to the deck below to avoid the poisonous gas, and you just catch a glimpse\nof the sorcerer as he frantically paddles a small boat away from the death-hulk\nflagship.",
