            "text": "You grasp the haft of the spear and level it at the approaching Helghast. It\nshrieks a desperate cry for it knows that it cannot avoid being impaled on the\nsharp tip of your spear. The shock of impact knocks you backwards and you crash\nto the highway below, losing 2 ENDURANCE points. The Helghast hits the ground\nbarely seconds later, driving the spear through its black heart, and dying\ninstantly.",
