        "339": {
            "text": "After only half an hour, the coach is stopped by some armed horsemen. They wear\nthe black ship and red crest emblem of Lachlan the Overlord of Ragadorn. They\ndemand gold in payment for what they call \"exit taxes\": one Crown from each\npassenger. The other travellers each place a Crown on a small plate and hand it\nto you.",
