        "344": {
            "text": "Your Kai sense reveals to you that the strangers are Helghast, fell captains of\nthe Darklords. They have been sent from the Darklord city of Helgedad on a\nmission of assassination. They have the ability to take on the appearance of\nhumans and they are immune to normal weapons and Mindblast.\n\nYou turn to shout a warning to Rhygar as you run for the safety of the forest.",
