                    "section": "183"
                }
            ]
        },
        "345": {
            "text": "A fierce battle now rages throughout the ship as the evil Giaks fight to win\ncontrol of the Green Sceptre. Perched high up in the masts, the Kraan are\nrending the sails with their talons and razor-sharp teeth whilst the Zlanbeast\nhave flown back towards Wreck Point to pick up more nets of malicious Giaks.\n\nThrough the body-strewn decks, a menacing shape looms. Both Giaks and sailors\nare cut down by the creature as it advances towards you. It is a Drakkar, a\ncruel warrior of the Darklords. Raising his jet-black broadsword, he attacks and\nyou must fight him to the death.\n\nDrakkar: COMBAT SKILL 16, ENDURANCE 24",
