        "346": {
            "must_eat": true,
            "text": "The driver nods and hands back the ticket. The inn is warm but poorly furnished.\nYou must eat a Meal here which will cost you 1 Gold Crown unless you have a Meal\nin your Backpack.\n\nThe Kai Discipline of Hunting cannot be used when instructed to eat a Meal on\nyour journey through the Wildlands, as it is a barren wasteland inhabited only\nby creatures called Szalls, a weak and cowardly breed of Giak.",
