                }
            ]
        },
        "348": {
            "text": "The sailor's face changes from a smile to a sneer at your reply. He quickly\nmoves away from the table.\n\n\"Perhaps neither you nor I are all we claim to be. No matter. You will not live\nlong enough to discover who I really am!\" You hear a door crash open behind you.\nSpinning round, you see three harbour thugs moving towards you. Each is armed\nwith a scimitar and you must fight them as one enemy.\n\nHarbour Thugs: COMBAT SKILL 16, ENDURANCE 25",
