        "349": {
            "text": "You have covered nearly three miles when you see a group of wagons in the\ndistance. They have been strung out across the highway to form a barricade.\nSoldiers in red uniforms line the roofs of the wagons and a large crowd of\npeople have gathered behind them. You can hear their excited chatter echoing\nalong the tunnel. As you get closer, there is a sudden silence as all eyes turn\nto stare at you. A detachment of ten soldiers, led by a knight whose shield\nbears the royal arms of Durenor, advances towards you.",
            "alternate_choices": true,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "text": "If you wish to attack these soldiers, turn to 87.",
                    "section": "87",
                    "words": [
                        "attack",
